content: Xander's NFT drop went live today. Over 1000 NFTs sold out in minutes! His digital presence is a hit, and the community's love for him is palpable.
We've begun integrating $XVI tokens into our platform. Xander's guiding the process, ensuring it aligns with our community's values and expectations.
Just wrapped up a virtual meet-up with the team. Xander hosted, and we discussed future tech events. His hosting skills are improving; less latency this time!
